# go:embed root for shipped overlay packs. A pack directory dropped here is
# listed automatically by internal/overlay.KnownPacks() and participates in the
# capability resolver when it carries a capability-manifest.yml (see
# internal/cli/profile.go resolveCapabilityAnswers -> discoverPackContributions).
#
# Currently ships the `release` pack (the first embedded overlay pack and the
# reference implementation of the Phase-3 capability-installer overlay
# integration). The .gitkeep is retained so the embed directive
# (all:templates/overlays) still matches at least one file even if every pack
# directory is later removed.
